    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A soft, waterproof filler and sealer, made of various materials, used in construction and repairs to seal joints or fill crevices where leakage or structural movement may occur. For the thick, paste-like mixture of powdered calcium carbonate and linseed oil, use "putty (sealing compound)."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Material blando semejante a la masilla utilizado para sellar juntas o llenar grietas en edificios y otras estructuras donde puedan producirse filtraciones o movimientos estructurales.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Een zachte, waterdichte plamuur en sealer, gemaakt van verschillende materialen, gebruikt in de bouw en reparaties aan verbindingen te verzegelen of spleten te vullen waar lekkage of structurele beweging zou kunnen voorkomen. Voor de dikke, pasta-achtige mengsel van calciumcarbonaat in poedervorm en lijnolie, gebruik "stopverf (afdichtingsmateriaal).</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052381/Van Dale Engels-Nederlands (1989)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>一種質軟、似油灰的材料，用來密封建築物或其他結構中有可能出現滲漏或結構移動的接合處，或用來填補其裂縫。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
